title: Mill Valley Kitchen
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Since late-2011. Restaurant and bar featuring Northern California inspired cuisine in a comfortable and refined setting. Uses fresh and local ingredients. Includes nutritional information for each menu item. Cuisine is light. Veg choices include a Mediterranean grain bowl, chili, gingered-shitake quinoa, sesame carrots, spicy green beans, roasted vegetables.
